"2022-08-01T09:00:05"},{"id":"01963dd4-7a05-71c5-902c-016544f11eb5","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":692,"content":"公司高管很会甩锅，想要确定个东西得所有人签字。","createdAt":"2022-08-05T17:16:56"},{"id":"01963dd4-7a50-71a9-8894-47bed93c9e77","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":154,"content":"我是工程部的，出去干活带几瓶公司的矿泉水都不让，某李姓人事","createdAt":"2022-08-05T17:24:42"},{"id":"01963dd4-7a96-71b9-8488-fb0857452fca","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":206,"content":"五月份的薪资现在还没发呢","createdAt":"2022-08-10T14:34:17"},{"id":"01963dd4-7af8-717c-9898-4e632832834c","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":206,"content":"五月份的薪资发了","createdAt":"2022-10-11T14:01:35"},{"id":"01963dd4-7b6a-70a1-80a7-1f635149c9c5","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":597,"content":"公司名牛逼","createdAt":"2022-10-19T15:55:49"},{"id":"01963dd4-7bb8-72c8-8fc4-e0cbbb5239d1","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":692,"content":"我们清了一位执行总裁，在他的带领下我们很快就能做大做强，然后挣大钱，把离职的家人的工资都补齐的。","createdAt":"2022-11-11T13:34:05"},{"id":"01963dd4-7c14-70f9-af25-386f8c6a1bd0","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":692,"content":"此用户已取消评论","createdAt":"2023-01-09T16:29:18"},{"id":"01963dd4-7bfd-7105-a6e8-a44e93cae1cb","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":691,"content":"我想知道在这位执行总裁的带领下有没有把离职的家人的工资补齐","createdAt":"2023-06-29T13:34:22"},{"id":"01963dd4-7c01-72b8-9a2b-b024f431391f","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":206,"content":"补齐了","createdAt":"2023-07-25T15:08:23"},{"id":"01963dd4-7c07-709f-957f-bbb189ddf223","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":1039,"content":"那很厉害啊","createdAt":"2023-07-25T15:51:17"},{"id":"01963dd4-7c57-72cb-95c7-38b4f1c2cc34","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":4016,"content":"龙帝软件注册资本5万(元)，玩儿呐","createdAt":"2023-07-25T16:07:05"},{"id":"01963dd4-7c0b-73f1-8bb2-ba9bfec3ad7c","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":154,"content":"仲裁补齐的","createdAt":"2023-08-18T09:20:19"},{"id":"01963dd4-7c9d-7033-b4bd-74e9d1a30721","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":692,"content":"龙帝还活着么？","createdAt":"2023-09-06T11:09:40"},{"id":"0